name: Audreyana Michelle
description:
Audreyana Michelle

Audreyana is an American fashion model. She is best known for opening Prada's A/W fashion show at 16 years old and walking in the Victoria's Secret Fashion Show 2018.

If you like my work, I'd appreciate it if you could Buy me a beer!

If you are interested in my creative process, you can read more in my blog post HERE.

And if you're feeling particularly curious, I can create a custom Textual Inversion or LoRA just for you!
